# Stack

## Minimal stack.yaml files

### GHC 8.0.2

~~~
resolver: lts-8.12
flags: {}
packages:
- '.'
extra-deps: []
~~~

### GHC 8.0.1

~~~
resolver: lts-7.19
flags: {}
packages:
- '.'
extra-deps: []
~~~

## Most important commands

### Setting up the stack environnement

    stack new    -- start from scratch

    stack init   -- start, when a cabal file is already here

### Building and compiling

    stack setup

    stack build

### Enabling intero

    stack build intero   -- must be done in every project !! 

